@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #ECEFF1
skinparam classBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBorderColor #455A64
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Active
Active --> Created : confirm
Created --> Closed : process
Closed --> OnHold : confirm
OnHold --> Reviewed : confirm
Reviewed --> Archived : confirm
Archived --> [*]
@enduml